name: testFixCoordinatorAccountTaskRunsOnCoordinatorLogin
description: Fix Admin Account task grants access to users on Coordinator login
descriptionHtml: Fix Admin Account task grants access to users on Coordinator login
statusMessage: This task no longer gives access to the team account (this is now redundant). It syncs keys for other team members to all other team admins. Setting this up in base data is actually a big faff - I need to add at least two more coordinators and then manually delete the keys and this entire mechanism is going away in my next PR. Lucian 2021-08
